=== Debugging Session (2026-04-20) ===

[*] Issue 1: CORS Rejection — Registration Blocked
    Root Cause: ALLOWED_ORIGINS env var is set as JSON array string:
        '["https://code-sentinal-chi.vercel.app","http://localhost:5173"]'
    But the parse_origins() validator in config.py split by comma,
    producing broken values with square brackets and quotes:
        ['["https://code-sentinal-chi.vercel.app"', '"http://localhost:5173"]']
    FastAPI CORS middleware rejected all origins since none matched.
    Fix: Updated parse_origins() to try json.loads() first for JSON arrays.
    Commit: 20ffb7d pushed to main, Render auto-deployed.
    Result: ✅ CORS fixed — requests now reach the backend (500 instead of CORS block).

[*] Issue 2: Database Tables Do Not Exist — 500 on Registration
    Error: asyncpg.exceptions.UndefinedTableError: relation "users" does not exist
