    The health check only runs SELECT 1 which works on an empty database.
    The Dockerfile only starts uvicorn — no migration step.
    Render Shell is paid — cannot run alembic upgrade head manually.
    Fix: Create startup script (start.sh) that runs alembic upgrade head
         before starting uvicorn. Update Dockerfile to use it.
    Status: Implementing now.

